{"tid":509914,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"老母成日亂掉我D野","createTime":"2017-12-26T00:24:42.000Z","updateTime":"2017-12-29T08:46:06.000Z","uid":91960,"like":24,"dislike":6,"uniUserReply":33,"replies":[{"pid":"da66e7984ec81741bb5345e1b991319512f8d525","tid":509914,"uid":91960,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-26T00:24:42.000Z","msg":"好撚燥<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> ，老母等我返工掉我細個D童年模型，最仆街係佢完全唔撚問我要唔要，on99掉左幾日先同我講翻，隻野我真係勁鐘意，我有keep住同佢換電同清潔架好冇，佢一句話冇用就掉9左，屌佢有冇尊重過我？我燥佢就只係識叫我搬岀去，掉我d野sorry都冇句。細個果陣已經成日掉同學送比我D文具，就係話我做功課唔尊心，而家我成22歲人佢仲係禁，試下比d尊重，問都唔問，屌仲要童年回憶黎架<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: red;\">究竟點先可以阻止佢個弱智行為？</span></strong></span><br />\n<br />\n利申間房唔亂"},{"pid":"3477adece06b1535d5b5b95ee598395a77b64751","tid":509914,"uid":64009,"like":6,"dislike":34,"score":-28,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2017-12-26T00:38:52.000Z","msg":"搬出去啦弱智<br />\n間屋你ga?<br />\n拋你若街都得踢dllm"},{"pid":"5ae2cb37b34cfb10cf62303aa495a2512f2e374c","tid":509914,"uid":12158,"like":20,"dislike":1,"score":19,"quote":{"pid":"3477adece06b1535d5b5b95ee598395a77b64751","tid":509914,"uid":64009,"like":6,"dislike":34,"score":-28,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2017-12-26T00:38:52.000Z","msg":"搬出去啦弱智<br />\n間屋你ga?<br />\n拋你若街都得踢dllm"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-26T00:44:00.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 多得你呢種人，共產黨先咁惡"},{"pid":"b1de24979ae25ba48e27896f132b4967b190e8bc","tid":509914,"uid":93867,"like":11,"dislike":0,"score":11,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-26T00:46:37.000Z","msg":"佢有無d 名牌袋，香水，或者好鍾意既野，你自己識做啦"},{"pid":"0f5011c86eb8233881ddafeedb1bc711efcf6354","tid":509914,"uid":59179,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-26T00:49:47.000Z","msg":"掉返佢啲野 or 報警拉佢 玩下佢都好"},{"pid":"08f6c13b31da68f6aa4034ae6e2ac180f9fa5b1f","tid":509914,"uid":61443,"like":24,"dislike":0,"score":24,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2017-1